data.description: Welcome home to 251 Cypress Dr! This one-level gem is ideally located just outside of town, yet within the sought-after Jackson School District. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, this 7-year-old home offers modern comfort and convenience. The spacious yard is perfect for kids to play in, and the move-in-ready condition makes it an ideal choice for first-time homebuyers. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Call to schedule your private showing today!
